node.text:
Photo-dump from my 10th birthday weekend. 😌🤍✨
Thank you all for your lovely messages and well wishes, you’ve made this old lady feel very special.
Thank you again to @rollsroycecars, @rollsroyce_quebec, @idateeri, and @shantell_design for making my champagne birthday such a success.
And a final thank you to everyone who submitted an entry to my design contest; it was an honour to see all the amazing concepts y’all came up with! 
Bisou! Tika 💕

node.text:
Celebrated my 10th birthday driving around town in a @rollsroycecars and wearing my birthday gown; now that’s how you do a champagne birthday! 🥂✨
Thank you @rollsroyce_quebec for my gorgeous chariot, @idateeri for designing my gorgeous gown, and @shantell_design for brining it to life.
#GhostDrive #RollsRoyce #tikatheiggy

node.text:
Turning 10 on the 10th, happy champagne birthday to me! I’m so excited to debut the winning outfit from my birthday design contest: congratulations to @idateeri! The biggest thank you to @shantell_design for bringing this design to life, I feel like the most gorgina kween; I’ll definitely be wearing this all day. 🤍✨
Thank you to everyone who participated, I had so much fun going through all the beautiful submissions. Now if you’ll excuse me, this old lady is off to get some botox. Bisou! 💕

node.text: To celebrate my 10th birthday week, my uncle @tristanbradock made me my very own batched craft cocktail, aptly titled “Italian Greyhound”! Made with gin, pisco, rose, curaçao, and grapefruit, I think that fits me to a tee! 💓🍾✨

node.text:
My dads are always telling me I have too much clothing, so I’ve decided it’s time to give some items a second life and help contribute to a more circular, sustainable future for fashion. If you’ve ever wanted to own a piece of my wardrobe, now’s your chance! I’ve listed some fun items from my closet on @poshmarkcanada. Poshmark is a social marketplace to buy, sell, and discover new and secondhand items, available in Canada, the US, and Australia.
✨ 100% proceeds from my closet will go to @rainbowrailroad.✨
Download Poshmark and use “TIKATHEIGGY” for C$15 off your first purchase. #TikaxPoshmark

node.text: I was feeling quite ill this past weekend, but after a lot of r&r (and a couple of trips to the vet), your girl is feeling tip-top shape! Hope y’all had a great weekend. Bisou xx

node.text:
I know it is a cliché, but please don’t interact with me before I’ve had my coffee.
Once said beverage is consumed, you may admire me, from a generous distance. 
That’s all.
Wearing custom @lucasstowebrand ✨
